This paper deals with the problem of detecting fake news on social media, which involves analyzing the propagation networks of news pieces. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), which deals with the analysis of social networks and information diffusion. The paper also involves analyzing the linguistic and structural features of news pieces, which suggests the category cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with social media, which suggests the category cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of fake news, which suggests the category cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
